## ğŸ”„ **Git Synchronization (Multi-machine)**

### **Initial Setup (One time)**

```bash
# Configure synchronization with private repository
devm sync setup git@github.com:your-username/devenv-private.git

# âœ… Output:
# ğŸ”§ Setting up git sync with git@github.com:your-username/devenv-private.git
# 
# â•­â”€ Sync Ready â”€â•®
